12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 74 O.S. 2021, Section 4258.1, is
14 amended to read as follows:
15 Section 4258.1. There is hereby created in the State Treasury a
16 revolving fund for the Ethics Commission to be designated the
17 "Political Subdivisions Enforcement Fund". The fund shall be a
18 continuing fund, not subject to fiscal year limitations, and shall
19 consist of all funds appropriated by the Legislature to the fund and
20 all late filing fees, fines from settlement agreements and fines
21 assessed by the District Court for violations of the County Campaign
22 Finance and Financial Disclosure Act, the Municipal Campaign Finance
23 and Financial Disclosure Act, and the Technology Center District and
24 Independent School District Campaign Finance and Financial
